item.title: MILITARY HUMMERS TRAILER 1.50 ATS
item.description:
MILITARY HUMMERS TRAILER 1.50 ATS

Military Hummers trailer by joao18wos. Updated to 1.50 by RussianGuy

You need to sleep a few times to argo appear! – Freight market (machinery). – Added license plate. – Added wheel particles. – Added Hummers shadows. – Added advance coupling system. – Added trailer cables system. – Corrected rear lights – Corrected axles height.


How to install ETS2 mods or ATS Mods

In Euro Truck Simulator 2 it’s easy to install mods. You just need to download mod from here, copy/unzip files into: “My Documents\Euro Truck Simulator 2\mod” folder or if you play ATS please install mods to: “My Documents\American Truck Simulator\mod” folder. To unzip files you can use: WinRAR or 7zip. After that you need to activate the mods you want to use.

item.title: Interior Cabin Lights 1.50 ATS
item.description:
Interior Cabin Lights 1.50 ATS

Added “90’s Corporation Truck” by TheOtherCorey Added support for Westernstar 5700 XE

This mod provides interior cabin-light glow in choice of blue, green, orange, purple, red, and white for SCS trucks and mod trucks listed below. Lights are available under “Driver’s Plate” and “Co-Driver’s Plate” in both (on w/Parking) and (Beacon switched) configurations; you can even mix them up: assign (on w/Parking) to one plate and (Beacon switched) to the other plate.

Note: If Options / Graphics / “Light visibility range” be Disabled, Interior Cabin Lights won’t work.
